high_descs: Turn around and walk to the back left corner of the room, by the black bench.
Pick up the credit card on the shelf.
Turn right and walk to the coffee table.
Put the credit card in the cardboard box.
Pick up the box.
Turn right and then hang left and go to the chair in the corner.
Put the box on the chair.
anns.task_desc: Put a box with a credit card in it on a chair.

high_descs: Turn around towards the other side of the room and look up to see the vase on the upper shelf.
Grab the credit card next to the vase.
Turn right, head towards the coffee table, stand in front of the opened box.
Place the card in the box.
Pick up the box with the card in it from the table.
Turn right, then turn left towards the sofa chair.
Place the box on the chair.
anns.task_desc: Place the box with the credit card on the leather chair.

high_descs: Turn around and head towards the brown shelf on the wall.
Take the credit card to the right of a vase on the shelf.
Turn right and walk to the coffee table on your right.
Place the credit card in the box on the table.
Pick up the box from the table.
Turn right, walk to the wall, and then turn left to the sofa chair.
Place the box on the chair.
anns.task_desc: Place the box with a credit card on the sofa chair.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the shelf in front of you.
Pick up the credit card on the shelf by your head.
Turn right and walk to the box that's on the table in front of you.
Put the credit card in the box.
Pick up the box with the credit card in it.
Turn right and walk to the wall then turn left and walk to the chair.
Put the box on the chair.
anns.task_desc: Put a box with a credit card in it on the chair.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the brown bench.
Pick up the credit card from the shelf above the brown bench.
Turn around and walk over to the table in the middle of the room with the open box.
Put the credit card inside the open box.
Pick up the box from the table.
Turn around and walk over to the chair on the other side of the room.
Put the box on the chair.
anns.task_desc: Place a box with a credit card inside on the chair.
